#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Which additional software can I install in Tails?"
msgstr "Welche zusätzliche Software kann ich in Tails installieren?"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails includes a [[limited set of applications|doc/about/features]] but you "
"can install more software."
msgstr ""
"Tails enthält bereits eine [[limited set of applications|doc/about/"
"features]], aber es kann weitere Software installiert werden."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This software is distributed in packages that are made available from the "
"Debian repositories, which are similar to an app store."
msgstr ""
"Diese Software wird in Paketen verteilt, die aus den Debian-Repositories "
"bereitgestellt werden, die einem App Store ähneln."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "To know which packages are available in Debian:"
msgstr "Eine Übersicht an Paketen, welche in Debian verfügbar sind:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Browse locally with the <span class=\"application\">Synaptic Package "
"Manager</span>:"
msgstr ""
"Suchen Sie lokal mit dem <span class=\"application\">Synaptic-"
"Paketverwaltung</span>:"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"When starting Tails, [[set up an administration password|doc/first_steps/"
"welcome_screen/administration_password]]."
msgstr ""
"Beim Starten von Tails [[richten Sie ein Administrationspasswort ein|doc/"
"first_steps/welcome_screen/administration_password]]."

#. type: Bullet: '    1. '
msgid ""
"Choose <span class=\"menuchoice\"> <span class=\"guimenu\">Applications</"
"span>&nbsp;▸ <span class=\"guisubmenu\">System Tools</span>&nbsp;▸ <span "
"class=\"guimenuitem\">Synaptic Package Manager</span></span>."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie <span class=\"menuchoice\"> <span class=\"guimenu\""
">Anwendung</span>&nbsp;▸ <span class=\"guisubmenu\""
">Systemprogramme</span>&nbsp;▸ <span class=\"guimenuitem\">Synaptic-"
"Paketverwaltung</span></span>."

#. type: Bullet: '  1. '
msgid ""
"Wait until <span class=\"application\">Synaptic</span> finishes downloading "
"new package information from the Debian servers."
msgstr ""
"Warten Sie, bis <span class=\"application\">Synaptic</span> das "
"Herunterladen neuer Paketinformationen von den Debian-Servern abgeschlossen "
"hat."

#. type: Bullet: '  1. '
msgid "You can:"
msgstr "Sie können:"

#. type: Bullet: '     - '
msgid "Browse the packages by sections from the left sidebar."
msgstr "Durchsuchen Sie die Pakete nach Abschnitten in der linken Seitenleiste."

#. type: Bullet: '     - '
msgid ""
"Search on titles and descriptions of packages with the <span "
"class=\"bold\">Search</span> button."
msgstr ""
"Suche in Titeln und Beschreibungen von Paketen mit der Schaltfläche <span "
"class=\"bold\">Suche</span>."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Search the Internet for alternatives to other software."
msgstr "- Suche im Internet nach Alternativen zu anderer Software."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  For example: \"*debian alternatives to photoshop*\".\n"
msgstr "  Zum Beispiel: \"*debian-Alternativen zu Photoshop*\".\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Ask a friend who is knowledgeable about Linux."
msgstr "- Fragen Sie einen Freund, der sich mit Linux auskennt."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- Search the [Debian website](https://www.debian.org/distrib/"
"packages#search_packages)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<a id=\"warning\"></a>\n"
msgstr "<a id=\"warning\"></a>\n"

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Be careful about what you install"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"caution\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"caution\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>The packages included in Tails are carefully tested for security.\n"
"Installing additional packages might break the security built in Tails. For\n"
"example, installing OpenVPN might modify the firewall rules that Tails uses to\n"
"force network traffic to go through Tor. So, be careful with what you\n"
"install.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>Die in Tails enthaltenen Pakete werden sorgfältig auf Sicherheit getestet."
"\n"
"Das Installieren zusätzlicher Pakete könnte die in Tails integrierte "
"Sicherheit beeinträchtigen.\n"
"Zum Beispiel könnte die Installation von OpenVPN die Firewall-Regeln ändern, "
"die Tails verwendet,\n"
"um den Netzwerkverkehr über Tor zu leiten. Seien Sie also vorsichtig, was "
"Sie installieren.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "If you are unsure:"
msgstr "Wenn Sie unsicher sind:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Packages that use the network need to be configured to go through Tor. They "
"are otherwise blocked from accessing the network."
msgstr ""
"Pakete, die das Netzwerk nutzen, müssen so konfiguriert werden, dass sie "
"über Tor geleitet werden. Andernfalls wird ihnen der Zugriff auf das "
"Netzwerk verwehrt."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Some software might, for example, modify the firewall and break the security "
"built in Tails. But other software like games or office tools are probably "
"fine."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Software not [[officially included in Tails|doc/about/features]] might have "
"not been tested for security.  We also cannot provide support or "
"documentation for it."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Only applications that are packaged for Debian can be installed and they are "
"under [[public scrutiny|doc/about/trust#trust_debian]]."
msgstr ""

